reviews.review_text: Decent recording, great show! Gotta love the fact that a split second after this woman yells a request for "Walk in the Sunshine!" the band opens with "Cold Rain and Snow". :-)

cool 76 been following 76 a bit lately, this is a real cool set list, nothing out of ordinary in the first set though it is quite good

second set is just great, love the song selection and the progression, really jammy with a space, spanish and stronger than dirt. cosmic charlie is great too
WALKIN ON SUNSHINE no ma'am, nuthin but cold rain and snow!! HILARIOUS.. its a great show and  worth the DL. i'm givin in 5 stars for the request snub, you th' man jerry
